name: Battle of Moscow - Test 1.0.1
description: September 30, 1941. Operation "Typhoon" has begun. German tank spearheads are ready to break through the Soviet defenses and encircle them. But the Soviet resistance is fierce, while they build fortifications and gather reinforcements. Will Moscow fall?

value.title: Breakthrough in the South!
value.message: On October 3, the German 2nd Tank Group succeeded in making a major breakthrough on the southern flank of the Bryansk Front. After advancing hundreds of kilometers, they managed to capture the city of Oryol completely defenceless.

value.title: Soviet Reinforcements from the Far East
value.message: On October 14th, the first echelons of Soviet divisions began to depart from the Far East. Japanese intelligence soon learned of this, but these reports were deemed false due to the known low throughput capacity of the Trans-Siberian Railway and disinformation efforts.

value.title: Moscow Militia
value.message: On October 11th, four Militia divisions were formed in Moscow.
